Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.63,0:01:49.75,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,So, what was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.75,0:01:51.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What was what about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:53.05,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Mei-chan's still around, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:55.76,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,It looked like you two were having fun yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:02:00.56,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,We spoke about what could be going on after seeing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.56,0:02:03.39,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I want to play with Mei-chan, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:06.64,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I want to let her listen to the violin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:09.11,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I think that's a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:11.98,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Kyou-chan's a bully.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:15.19,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Mei-chan's worried about Sunohara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:17.28,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We talked about it last night, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:20.03,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,But I think that's the only chance. {ep 3}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.58,0:02:26.25,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,If he plays soccer again,\Nmaybe he'll return to the way he used to be. {ep 3}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:28.00,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Huh? Talk about the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:31.88,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,There's no way he could return to the soccer team now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:33.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I told her the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:38.72,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You know well what kind of group our Soccer Team is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:42.14,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,It's best you stay away from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:46.85,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Yes, since our school's Soccer Team is a little special.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:48.81,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Are they bullies?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:53.11,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,For once, your pet phrase actually fits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:56.78,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(957.273,415.8)}Episode 4
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:56.78,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(960,712.5)}With the Same Smile as That Day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:58.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He wasn't in the dorm, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:03.20,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,No. Even Misae-san doesn't know where he went.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:08.58,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What should we do? Without the actual person, we can't ask them to let him rejoin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:11.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Mei-chan, let's think it over. {ep3}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:14.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I think the chance of this working is slim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:19.55,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I'll go on ahead and ask them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:21.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,"Go ahead", as in to the Soccer Team?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:24.89,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Yes. You two wait here please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.43,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I'll go by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:27.73,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:29.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How could we let you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:32.15,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,If you're going to go, then we will, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:43.41,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Did you just say Sunohara Youhei?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Winter's the critical season for high school soccer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:49.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Even a senior should be able to participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:52.08,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Could you let him play again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:54.29,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Shut your trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:56.67,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,We don't even want to hear his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:57.55,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:58.13,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Um!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:02.01,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,My name is Mei, Sunohara Youhei's younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:05.18,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Sunohara's younger sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:08.18,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I'm aware how my brother has caused trouble to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:09.89,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,But please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:12.85,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,At this rate, I think he will become a loafer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:13.56,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,So!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:17.02,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,He was a loafer to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:21.15,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,Yeah. A loafer will always be\Na loafer no matter what he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:26.12,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,Okazaki. You're the same as him,\Nso don't you understand that logic?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:28.29,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,And you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:31.50,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,You're repeating a grade and are an outcast, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:36.34,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,Loafers should hang out with loafers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:38.63,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:48.18,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sorry. I should have gone there alone first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:51.27,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:53.94,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Both of you had to suffer because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:57.02,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No, we're fine. Rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:59.19,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Would you like another cup, Mei-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:02.15,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:04.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sorry we're imposing on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:09.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I had a feeling you would listen to something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:11.16,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I'm completely fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:16.17,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Since I have guests with an assortment of problems needing advice come here often.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:20.96,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:27.68,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,If it's all right, would you share what happened between Sunohara-san and the Soccer Team?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:30.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Can I, Mei-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.98,0:05:36.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He started a fight when he was a freshman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:45.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Our school's Soccer Team has a tradition of underclassmen being hazed by upperclassmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:49.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The hierarchy within the team is atrocious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:59.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Apparently Sunohara couldn't stand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:06.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The first time I met him was then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:13.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I got in a fight somewhere else and bumped into him near the faculty room, and we've been hanging out since.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.56,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I never knew that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:20.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Because of the fight, the team had to withdraw from the rookie tournament that year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:23.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sunohara left the team afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:27.91,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,So the Soccer Team hasn't forgotten what happened then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.91,0:06:33.66,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,If so, would Sunohara-san be able to enjoy playing soccer in an environment like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:35.54,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:39.67,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,But soccer's the only way to get Onii-chan back to who he used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:45.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But there's no point in us getting worked up when he's not around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:48.18,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,He's so hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:52.39,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,Have I ever told you the story of my older brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:56.14,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You have an older brother, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:07:01.90,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,My brother would not go to school; instead he'd loiter around party town and constantly get into fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:05.40,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,He was detained by the police several times, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:07.99,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Your brother was?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:08.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I never would have guessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.66,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,Siblings can be strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:15.66,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,But you like your brother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:22.17,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,I used to think of him as a scary person, but I understand him well now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:27.92,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,He has many good traits\Nbut just can't express them well. {ep3}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:31.18,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,He was simply clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:34.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sanae-san described Sunohara like that, too, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:41.06,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,I think, too, that Sunohara-san has many good traits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:48.07,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,Even if it's not with soccer, given the chance, he'll be the brother you used to love again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:51.61,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,What is it like now between you and your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:53.57,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,We get along very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:04.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sunohara, what were you doing yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:06.88,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,It's my business what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:09.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You don't care about what Mei-chan's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.39,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Why are you even asking that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:13.84,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Mei was with you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:17.56,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'm busy taking care of matters with Sanae-san. {ep3}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:19.81,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I don't have time to worry about Mei. {ep3}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:22.73,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Do you seriously mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:24.52,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:26.15,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'll leave Mei to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:27.57,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Make sure you take good care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:31.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You'd better quit it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:32.74,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What are you angry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:34.66,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I bet Mei doesn't care about me either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:35.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,SUNOHARA!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:39.62,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Okazaki-kun! Sunohara-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:41.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What do you think Mei-chan's doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:42.58,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:44.75,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,But I bet you and her are having a good time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:47.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ask the Soccer Team yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:50.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,They'll tell you how much she's thinking about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:53.80,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:54.97,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You're not making any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:57.18,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Please stop, Okazaki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:08:58.97,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:02.48,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You wanna fight, Okazaki? {ep3}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:06.06,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Break it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:08.11,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,What's this about? What's the reason for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:10.11,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,What happened, Ryou-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:11.82,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I'm not sure, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:15.66,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun, Sunohara-kun.\NI don't think fighting is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:19.24,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Tomoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:20.20,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:25.17,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Sunohara-kun, really, what is the matter here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:29.71,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,So you got in a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:32.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah. I lost my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:34.13,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,What's Onii-chan doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:36.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He skipped afternoon classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:38.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He must have gone out to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.72,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:41.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you going to the Soccer Team again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:47.73,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Yes. After hearing Miyazawa-san's story, I feel like I have to keep trying harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:51.69,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I can go alone, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:55.36,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I can't trouble you any more with this sibling matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:57.57,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's no trouble at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:10:00.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No. Nagisa, you go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:02.33,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:04.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You know what kind of a bunch the Soccer Team is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:07.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We don't know how the meeting may get twisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:09.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Just Mei-chan and I should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.13,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I won't allow that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:13.76,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I can't let just the two of you go after hearing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:16.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What would you do if they started to get violent?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:19.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If it turns into a fight, I won't be able to cover you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:26.44,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,If that happens, I'll run away with Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:30.73,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Even if anything were to happen to you,\Nif I'm there, I can get Mei-chan out of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:36.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You really are stubborn when it comes to something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.41,0:10:40.32,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,You guys really don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:42.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We're asking knowing it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:46.08,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Please let Sunohara-san back on the team!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:48.25,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,It's fine if he can't play in the games.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:50.46,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Just letting him participate in practice is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:54.51,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey! Do you see anything in it for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:57.47,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,We'll just get an extra obstacle on the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.47,0:11:00.89,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,If there's anything I can help with, please let me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:01.85,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.81,0:11:05.31,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Captain, let's start practicing already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:08.23,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Forget about them and please get over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:08.81,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.44,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:12.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We know we're being unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:13.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:14.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We're begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:19.95,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:23.08,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I never imagined Okazaki would beg like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:26.70,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I heard that you'd changed recently, but I guess the rumor was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.33,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:31.58,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Go be a ball boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:33.84,Default,2,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:36.55,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Okazaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:38.63,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,That was very admirable of you, Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:40.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It wasn't much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:42.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Rather than that, let's do our best as ball boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:42.97,Default,2,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:59.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't overexert yourself, since you're not very strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:00.28,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:02.95,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Please watch out for Mei-chan over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:06.41,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Go get it, ball boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:07.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:12.50,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Don't space out, ball boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:13.46,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:17.00,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Get a move on, airhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:18.67,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:25.72,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,You dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.81,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Bring it back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:29.73,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:32.39,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,There goes another!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:35.15,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Come on! Hurry and go get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:35.86,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:38.44,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Move faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:39.65,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:40.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,They're doing it on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:42.78,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Tired already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:51.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa, Mei-chan, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.46,0:12:53.42,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:55.54,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I'm fine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:00.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You guys catch your breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:05.34,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Mei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:08.60,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:11.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Those guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:15.40,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,No. It's because I wasn't paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:17.15,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Mei-chan, you should...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:19.40,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.53,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,That was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:26.62,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Stop wasting time, trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.62,0:13:27.49,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:37.50,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,We're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:39.17,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:41.67,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um, where did the other members go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:42.63,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,They went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:46.26,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Practice is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:49.60,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,We'll listen to what you guys have to say for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:52.02,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,So, what did you guys want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:55.14,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,About my brother, Sunohara Youhei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:56.98,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,We would like you to let him back on the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:59.15,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry. Don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:05.15,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Who would let a pest like your brother onto the team?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:07.20,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,He is a wuss, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:10.74,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,A loser that just barks when he's got no balls to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:15.41,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,A dropout that quit soccer and can't study for beans either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:20.13,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Where's the reason in helping a piece of trash like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:21.46,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,How could you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:22.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:30.05,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Did you guys know that Sunohara knows what you guys are doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:33.72,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Apparently he asked one of our younger guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:34.77,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,But so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:37.48,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Your brother didn't show up at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:39.19,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,You've been ignored.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:44.07,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Despite what his sister's doing for him, he got scared of us and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:47.28,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,He is a hopeless piece of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:50.41,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:52.28,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Aw, you made her cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:54.29,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,You're becoming an eyesore now. Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.29,0:14:56.08,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,No... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:57.71,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Onii-chan will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.71,0:14:59.04,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,He'll definitely come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:00.67,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,What won't come won't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:02.67,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,He will. Onii-chan will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:06.05,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,He'll definitely come save Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:07.55,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:09.64,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Huh? Is she an absolute moron?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:12.60,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,She is Sunohara's sister, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:16.35,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Here, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:21.10,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,If you don't scream louder,\Nyour dear Onii-chan won't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.73,0:15:18.10,Default-alt,Mei,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:21.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:22.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:23.32,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:25.94,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,You want to start a fight with all of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:27.53,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Cry louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:28.40,Default-alt,Mei,0,0,0,,Th-That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:30.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:31.45,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:36.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sorry, Nagisa. I was planning on holding it in for Mei-chan's sake, but I'm at my limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:40.54,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:43.75,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Come on! Cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:56.10,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Don't make Mei cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:16:01.73,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I won't forgive anyone who makes Mei cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:02.56,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:07.90,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:08.61,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sunohara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:17.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa, take care of Mei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:18.50,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:20.83,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Onii-chan! Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:22.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't forget I'm here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:38.64,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,You guys are insane...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.02,0:16:40.93,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,They've got crazy eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:44.56,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okazaki... Did we win?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:46.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:48.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But I don't think we lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:51.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:53.24,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Who are you calling an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:56.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Who else other than you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.29,0:16:59.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Apologize to Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:02.37,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:06.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,This never would have happened if you'd kept yourself right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:08.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You really are a worthless brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:11.63,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Are you picking a fight with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:14.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Basically.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:22.81,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:23.98,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sunohara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:26.56,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Stop! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You flaming idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:44.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Do you have any clue what Mei-chan went through because of you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:47.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You have to be the one to look after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:49.96,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:51.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're Mei-chan's brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:54.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Think more of Mei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:54.88,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:56.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't lie to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:18:00.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She was hooking up to a guy like me,\Nand you didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You didn't worry about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:03.18,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:04.39,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I sure did!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:06.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then why did you leave her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:08.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If you have an excuse, say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:10.86,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I thought it was fine if it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:16.82,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I was planning on hiding and watching to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:20.08,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,But because you were being so pathetic, I had to come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.08,0:18:22.33,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun! Sunohara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:24.29,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Please stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:26.62,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You should have protected Mei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:29.42,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Isn't that the boyfriend's role?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:30.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:32.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sunohara!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:37.63,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You love Mei enough to break up with Nagisa-chan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:39.89,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Then get your goddamn act together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:43.85,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Onii-chan! Okazaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:46.39,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Please stop this, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:49.19,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Nagisa-chan? Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:52.36,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You've done it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:54.28,Default-alt,Mei,0,0,0,,Stop it! Please stop it now, Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:56.70,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Onii-chan! Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:59.16,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:00.32,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Mei...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:19.30,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you take a day off from school?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:23.60,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Aren't you the one who's still tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:25.81,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:50.25,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,What happened to your eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:51.29,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,They look horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:53.04,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,But they look like they're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:02.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We got a letter from Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:04.26,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Not just a phone call, but a letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:06.81,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,She really has a keen sense of duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:09.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She asked me to take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:14.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,And she also said she wants to find great friends just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:19.44,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's often said that you're forever stuck with the friends you make during your school days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:24.70,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I bet now's the only time you can do stupid things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:26.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:30.04,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Just six more months left at this high school, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:36.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There's the old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:39.42,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Crap. I'm starting to get really nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:40.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Do you want to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:42.26,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,No, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:45.60,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Since the only woman I love is Sanae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:48.18,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okay. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.93,0:20:50.93,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:53.60,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Oh, ah... Sunohara, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:55.48,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What? Are you here to buy bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:58.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Father! Please give Sanae-san to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:02.70,San,San,0,0,0,,What's going on, Akio-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.41,0:21:04.45,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,"Akio-san"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:09.62,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun, you haven't told Sunohara-san about Mom yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:11.16,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,"M-Mom"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:11.71,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:14.42,San,San,0,0,0,,Akio-san is my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:20.30,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You sunuva... You dare touch my woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:22.67,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:28.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I was remembering the first time I met Sunohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:43.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He was a weird blond guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:46.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I cracked up just looking at his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:50.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It was my first time laughing so much since coming to this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:55.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I wanted to try doing stupid things with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.33,0:22:01.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,From the day we met, we've hung out ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:04.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,And even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.22,0:22:06.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We're still smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.74,0:23:43.73,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\pos(981.818,452.25)\c&HFFFFFF&\be2\4c&H000000&\3c&H454845&\bord3.15}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.43,0:23:43.23,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Yeah, what a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.60,0:23:45.64,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,You know, if you don't mind-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.64,0:23:46.56,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.31,0:23:49.23,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Looks like he's from a different school.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.11,0:23:51.90,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,...because of you, he misunderstood!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.48,0:23:55.28,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There are a lot of guys who are fans of yours in my class, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.82,0:23:57.95,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,It's great that I'm liked,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.37,0:24:01.74,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,but I don't know what they see in a woman who only yells.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.74,0:24:05.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,In this dirty boy's dorm,\Nyou've become an idol-like figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.08,0:24:07.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Like a jewel in a dunghill.
